      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DANCEWITHME (5) bolted in on her return to the races, flying late to run away from her rivals by 2.3L. She resumed without a trial as well, so there may still be plenty of improvement to come with her. The splits she ran were very quick last start and this shapes similarly. Can get back in the run and storm over the top. SHOW THE WAY (2) just missed in a stronger race at Bunbury last time out when running on from midfield. He looks to get plenty of favours again today from a good draw and while he hasn't won for a long time, he's right on the verge. Can end the drought today. ROAMING AMERICA (1) picked up his maiden win last start at Ascot over 1000m and did so in good fashion. Out to 1200m now and he can launch again third-up into the campaign. Can repeat the dose. SEASTIC (6) will find this a little easier than her last start and can make her presence felt. GINGERBREAD GIRL (9) can bounce back to her best out to 1200m.",
